        <h2>Check if an account exists within a certain phone number:</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Telegram:</strong> <a href="https://t.me/+123456789" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://t.me/+123456789</a> (Need Telegram installed - desktop)</li>
          <li><strong>WhatsApp:</strong> <a href="http://wa.me/+123456789" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">http://wa.me/+123456789</a> (Need WhatsApp installed - desktop)</li>
          <li><strong>Viber:</strong> <a href="http://viber.click/+123456789" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">http://viber.click/+123456789</a></li>
          <li><strong>Facebook:</strong> Search Accounts with Phone Number</li>
